3 misdemeanor punishable by a fine not to exceed Five Hundred Dollars
4 ($500.00), or by imprisonment in the county jail for not more than
5 one (1) year, or by both such fine and imprisonment. Nothing in
6 this section shall prevent a judge from ordering restitution for any
7 damage caused by a driver involved in an accident provided for in
8 this section.
9 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
10 Passed the Senate the 18th day of February, 2026.
